{
  "texts": [
    "Various teaching methodologies must be examined in various educational contexts for further exploration.",
    "In conclusion, while there has been considerable progress in STEM education research in China, there remains a critical need for comprehensive, diversified, and methodologically diverse research to understand and fully improve STEM teacher professional development.",
    "Such research is essential for addressing the gaps identified and ensuring that TPD programs effectively enhance STEM education across different contexts in China (see Fig. 1).",
    "Theoretical framework.",
    "This study is grounded in the concept of adult learning theory, as discussed by Kleinke and Lin (2020), which is crucial for understanding the professional growth of STEM teachers."
  ]
}